StarFlier::

She looked at the coccoon.  "Hmm, well, the only way to find out is 
to open it."  She pulled out a long dragon claw dagger and 
smiled. "Well, we can slowly take the layers away and find what's in 
the middle. What do you say? Or if you have ice capability, we can 
freeze the outside and smash the ice away and see what's in the 
middle that way?"
